dren from his prior marriages among peltzs children are actors nicola peltz and will peltz his son brad peltz was a professional ice hockey player who played in the echl during the – echl season peltz resides in bedford new york he also owns montsorrel which is his house in palm beach florida previously owned by anita young the sister of georgia okeeffe he has recently begun a refurbishment and expansion project for the property wealth and philanthropyedit according to forbes magazine he has a net worth of  billion as of february  this makes him the nd richest person in the us in  peltz was among  entities that contributed the maximum of  to the second inauguration of president george w bush he is also a heavy contributor to jewish causes awards and recognitionedit he was recognized by the national association of corporate directors nacd in   and  as among the most influential people in global corporate governance referencesedit  a b nelson peltzs house virtualglobetrottingcom retrieved february     a b forbes the worlds billionaires nelson peltz february   a b c duane d stanford january   mondelez names peltz director as investor seen pushing cuts bloomberg   a b anupreeta das and sharon terlep august   activist peltz wins board seat at ingersoll the wall street journal   a b biography nelson peltz wendys retrieved april     a b shawn tully march   the reinvention of nelson peltz cnnmoneycom   company overview of trian fund management lp bloomberg businessweek retrieved april     fortune  fortune magazine retrieved april     a b c d jewish virtual library nelson peltz by nancy a ruhling retrieved january    maurice peltz  built family food business into a major marketer the new york times    paid notice deaths peltz claire the new york times    wall street frats business insider retrieved  february    a b katherine burton and sree vidya bhaktavatsalam september   peltz gets  billion as activist strategy impresses bloomberg news   palm beach daily news matisse  the 