oints in operating margin over the past four years at the same time pg is committed to continued productivity improvement and cost savings that provide the fuel for innovation and investments needed to accelerate and sustain faster topline growth for example the company will reinvest savings to improve product formulations and packaging sales coverage and media programs as well as product sampling and instore and online demand creation pg will also invest in consumer value equations correcting value gaps and quickly responding to competitive challenges as they emerge throughout the year if you liked this article you might like dont buy the hype twitter isnt dead yet att verizon prove their worth heres what you need to know now michael brown jul    am edt nasdaq tumbles as tech takes a turn lower the nasdaq tumbles and the sp  slides the dow rises slightly keris alison lahiff jul    pm edt jim cramer on facebook twitter comcast verizon southwest airlines procter  gamble paypal and exxon mobil thestreets action alerts plus portfolio manager jim cramer sheds light on thursdays trending stocks scott gamm jul    am edt heres what procter  gambles ceo had to say about his new activist investor squeaky clean lindsay rittenhouse jul    am edt trending tesla is a cult stock jim cramer says amazon alphabet and a gop failure on healthcare heres where wall street stands ipod nano shuffle are dead here are  other discontinued apple products heres why snaps stock could be in for another big plunge on monday can apple show amazon what earnings should look like advertising partners  thestreet inc all rights reservedaction alerts plus is a registered trademark of thestreet inc compare brokers trian fund management lp private company information  bloomberg july    pm et capital markets company overview of trian fund management lp snapshot people company overview trian fund management lp is a privately owned hedge fund sponsor the firm provides its services to pooled investment vehicles and single investor investment vehicles it launches and manages hedge funds it primarily invests in public equity and alterative investment markets across the globe the firm invests in undervalued stocks and employs fundamental analysis to create its portfolio trian fund management lp was founded in  and is based in new york city  park avenuest floornew york ny united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwtrianpartnerscom key executives for trian fund management lp mr nelson peltz founding partner and chief executive officer age  mr peter william may mba founding partner and president age  mr edward patrick garden founding partner and chief investment officer age  mr gregory alan essner cpa chief financial officer and partner age  mr brian lewis schorr jd chief legal officer and partner age  compensation as of fiscal year  trian fund management lp key developments trian fund management lp presents at niri annual conference jun  am jun   trian fund management lp presents at niri annual conference jun  am venue grande lakes orlando jw marriott  ritzcarlton orlando florida united states speakers brian lewis schorr chief legal officer and partner trian fund management lp presents at nd annual corporate governance conference jun may   trian fund management lp presents at nd annual corporate governance conference jun venue jw marriott essex house new york new york united states presentation date  speakers jun edward patrick garden founding partner and chief investment officer matthew h peltz partner and senior analyst trian fund management lp presents at th annual shareholder activism conference nov nov   trian fund management lp presents at th annual shareholder activism conference nov  venue new york new york united states speakers josh frank similar private companies by industry company name region visory llc united states  road partners llc united states t partners llc united states jumpcom inc united states  ontario inc united states recent private companies transactio